sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Router as TGIS Router (Rust)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC TLS/mTLS
    participant HTTP as TGIS Router (Rust)<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant Shard0 as Python Shard 0<br/>UDS plaintext
    participant ShardN as Python Shard N<br/>UDS plaintext
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA 12.1
    participant NCCL as NCCL<br/>29500/TCP plaintext

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation (gRPC)
    Client->>KServe: POST gRPC Generate<br/>TLS 1.2+
    KServe->>Router: Forward gRPC<br/>TLS/mTLS (8033/TCP)
    Router->>Router: Validate request<br/>(max tokens, sequence length)
    Router->>Router: Tokenize input<br/>(HuggingFace tokenizer)
    Router->>Router: Batch queue<br/>(continuous batching)
    Router->>Shard0: Prefill RPC<br/>gRPC over UDS
    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA forward pass
    Shard0->>NCCL: allreduce (multi-GPU)
    NCCL->>ShardN: Tensor parallel sync
    ShardN->>NCCL: allreduce result
    NCCL->>Shard0: Aggregated result
    loop NextToken loop (until EOS or max_new_tokens)
        Router->>Shard0: NextToken RPC<br/>gRPC over UDS
        Shard0->>GPU: CUDA forward pass
        Shard0->>NCCL: allreduce (multi-GPU)
        NCCL-->>Shard0: Aggregated result
    end
    Shard0-->>Router: Generated tokens
    Router-->>KServe: gRPC Response<br/>TLS/mTLS
    KServe-->>Client: Response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: Streaming Text Generation (gRPC)
    Client->>KServe: gRPC GenerateStream<br/>TLS 1.2+
    KServe->>Router: Forward stream<br/>TLS/mTLS (8033/TCP)
    Router->>Router: Validate + Tokenize
    Router->>Shard0: Prefill RPC<br/>gRPC over UDS
    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA forward pass
    Router-->>Client: Stream first token
    loop NextToken loop (streaming)
        Router->>Shard0: NextToken RPC<br/>gRPC over UDS
        Shard0->>GPU: CUDA forward pass
        Router-->>Client: Stream each token
    end

    Note over Client,HTTP: Flow 3: Health Check
    Client->>HTTP: GET /health<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    HTTP->>Shard0: Health RPC<br/>gRPC over UDS
    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA alloc test
    GPU-->>Shard0: GPU available
    Shard0-->>HTTP: Healthy
    HTTP-->>Client: 200 OK
